Let $$f\colon M \to \R^3$$ be a regular parametrized surface with [[Levi-Civita connection |Levi-Civita connection (surfaces)]]$$\nabla$$ and [[shape operator|Shape operator]] $$A.$$ Then
$$
(\nabla_X A)Y = (\nabla_Y A)X.
$$